constraints_details.result: Hinterland Lower Lea Valley including Stratford

description: Erection of a part 12, part 44 storey 54,778 sqm building to provide 484 flats, 323 sqm of retail floorspace (Use Class A1), a 948 sq m Health and Fitness club (Use Class D2) , an ancillary concierge facility together with associated landscaping, car parking, servicing and plant. The application is accompanied by an Environmental Impact Assessment pursuant to the Town And Country Planning (Environmental Impact Assessment) Regulations 1999.
